OL,3,CAnimal sanctuary owner gets life ban
OL,4,Cfor 'one of worst neglect cases ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FAn animal sanctuary owner has been
OL,8,Fbanned from keeping animals for life
OL,9,Fafter an investigation found she kept
OL,10,Fthem in appalling conditions.
OL,12,FTamara Lloyd, who owned and ran the
OL,13,FAlternative Animal Sanctuary in New
OL,14,FYork, near Boston, saw her sentence
OL,15,Fincreased after appealing her previous
OL,16,Fconvictions.
OL,18,FMore than 70 cats, 14 pigs, along with
OL,19,Fdogs, horses and terrapins were among
OL,20,Fthe animals kept in awful conditions.
