OL,7,FThe RSPCA executed two separate
OL,8,Fwarrants in May 2019 and January 2020
OL,9,Fafter concerns were raised about the
OL,10,Fwelfare of animals in her care.
OL,12,FPC Martin Green of the Rural Crime
OL,13,FAction Team at Lincolnshire Police
OL,14,Fsaid: "This is not sadistic behaviour,
OL,15,Fbut it is driven by your unshakeable
OL,16,Fbelief that all experts are wrong and
OL,17,Fyou are the only person who knows and
OL,18,Funderstands you animals.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
