OL,7,F"This led to prolonged and repeated
OL,8,Fincidents of neglect and deliberate
OL,9,Fdisregard to the welfare of the
OL,10,Fanimals.
OL,12,F"This was one of the worst cases of
OL,13,Fneglect involving animals I have seen
OL,14,Fin many years, mainly due to the
OL,15,Fnumber of animals that were present,
OL,16,Fwith only one person responsible for
OL,17,Ftheir welfare."
