OL,3,CAnimal sanctuary owner gets life ban
OL,4,Cfor 'one of worst neglect cases ever
OL,5,Cseen'
OL,7,FIn 2020, she was convicted of 17
OL,8,Fanimal welfare offences, following an
OL,9,Finvestigation and prosecution by the
OL,10,FRSPCA. She was then given a ten year
OL,11,Fdisqualification order.
OL,13,FLloyd launched an appeal but has seen
OL,14,Fher sentence increased after losing in
OL,15,Fcourt.
OL,17,FShe was given a life ban and ordered
OL,18,Fto pay #65,000. She was sentenced to
OL,19,Feight months in prison, suspended for
OL,20,Ftwo years, at Lincoln Crown Court on
OL,21,F27 September.
